&lt;p>&#xD;
    Capability Improvement metrics help an organization monitor and steer their software or systems delivery&#xD;
    capabilities.&amp;nbsp; As operational objectives are identified, metrics mapped to specific strategies and solutions are&#xD;
    collected to measure improvement.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    While&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;elementLink&quot;&#xD;
    href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/customcategories/project_execution_metrics_C29D56DC.html&quot;&#xD;
     guid=&quot;_Y_xjcLQoEd6HgZ8EwRW1Og&quot;>Project Execution Metrics&lt;/a> indicate how well&amp;nbsp;a particular&amp;nbsp;project&#xD;
    is&amp;nbsp;doing, Capability Improvement metrics indicate how well&amp;nbsp;an organization's&amp;nbsp;process is working.&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
    Capability Improvement metrics are identified for each practice adopted by the organization and can be mapped to one or&#xD;
    more of the five &lt;a class=&quot;elementLink&quot;&#xD;
    href=&quot;./../../practice.bus.perf_meas_setup.base-ibm/guidances/concepts/dimensions_of_delivery_efficiency_9B17FFE5.html&quot;&#xD;
    guid=&quot;_3i9Y8LQoEd6HgZ8EwRW1Og&quot;>Dimensions of Delivery Efficiency&lt;/a>:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;strong>Time to&amp;nbsp;Delivery&lt;/strong> - Are we reducing the time spent on delivering our systems?&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;strong>Value&lt;/strong> - Do the systems we build increase stakeholder business value?&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;strong>Cost&lt;/strong> - Are we reducing costs in building systems?&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;strong>Quality&lt;/strong> - Are the systems we build of higher quality?&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;strong>Predictability&lt;/strong> - Are we getting better at dealing with uncertainty?&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
    &amp;nbsp;&#xD;
&lt;/p>
